---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="ISPC Volunteer" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">ISPC Volunteer Shift Lead</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <img src="/ispc.jpg" alt="ISPC Community" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-xl mb-8" />

    <div class="text-lg text-justify">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Mission</h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Since 2024, I have served as a Shift Lead for the Islamic Society of Pinellas County during critical community service events. This role involves managing the logistics of large-scale gatherings (100+ daily attendees) and ensuring the safety and comfort of community members. It requires rapid problem-solving and the ability to maintain composure in a high-traffic environment.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Leadership & Impact</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Team Coordination:</strong> Directed a rotating team of 10+ youth volunteers, assigning roles based on individual strengths to maximize efficiency.</li>
        <li><strong>Crisis Management:</strong> Resolved logistical conflicts and interpersonal issues on the ground, ensuring a seamless experience for attendees.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Health:</strong> Oversaw food distribution protocols, prioritizing hygiene and speed to serve large groups within tight time constraints.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="alert alert-info shadow-lg mt-6">
        <div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          <span>"This role honed the empathy and leadership skills I plan to bring to my future dental practice."</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
